    "name": "Garden Grove MMA Tank Leak",
    "facility": "GKN Aerospace, Garden Grove, CA",
    "started_iso": "2026-05-21T22:40:00Z",
    "status_headline": "Incident fully resolved \u2014 all evacuation orders lifted May 27 at 7:30 PM PDT. No chemical leak, explosion risk, or fire threat. Tank temperature stabilizing at 90\u00b0F; water cooling deactivated. Hazmat crews treating solidified MMA in 300-ft exclusion zone on Western Ave. GGUSD schools reopened today (final day of school year). Evacuation shelters closed. DA criminal investigation, class-action lawsuits, and Rep. Tran town hall demanding state/federal accountability all ongoing.",
